{"tid":663094,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港男租車遊台撞爛走數　苦主發最後通牒 起底吧！","createTime":"2018-05-13T04:02:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-13T16:59:58.000Z","uid":72009,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"0459149a50dd689e67efa3da39c1a9419e4e8fb4","tid":663094,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T04:02:43.000Z","msg":"台灣一名租車公司負責人上周六（12日）在Facebook專頁「爆料公社」發文稱，一名鄧姓的香港男子上月到台灣自駕遊時，撞爛了租車公司一架170萬元（新台幣．下同，約45.4萬港元）的新車，維修費用估計達70萬元（約18.7萬港元）。鄧男當時刷親戚的信用卡賠了25萬元（約6.6萬港元），惟回港後竟向銀行申請取消交易。負責人怒斥鄧男「丟盡了香港人的臉」，並向《東網》記者表示願意給鄧男一個機會，希望兩天後對方會有所回應，否則將採取必要行動。 <br />\n<br />\n租車公司的游姓負責人稱，鄧男上月2日向其公司租了一輛福士T6客貨車，當晚就在宜蘭的礁溪自撞，令車輛嚴重損毀。鄧男當時要求再租另一同款汽車繼續行程，還表示「很幸運承租德國的車系，家人平安」。對於賠償一事，鄧男就自稱無錢，堅持要回港才一次過賠款，但租車公司未有同意。 <br />\n<br />\n後來在萬華區警方的協解下，鄧男在派出所刷親戚的信用卡支付了小部分賠款，並簽下理賠協議書，承諾會支付餘下的款項。未料鄧男回港之後，竟向發卡銀行申請停止交易，請銀行代為追回款項，同時又在通訊軟件上把租車公司加入黑名單。 <br />\n<br />\n「這位香港人在台灣旅遊糟蹋了我們台灣人的財產，然後用詐騙的手段說家人會簽名，結果食言！」游姓負責人表示，自己正研究採取法律行動，以及向媒體爆出事件的始末，「我將按照你（鄧男）所簽名的租車條款，向法院聲請賠償車子的損失！這將會暴增賠償費用！」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180513/mobile/bkn-20180513040419881-0513_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180513%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20180513040419881-0513_00822_001.html&d=XeGbOuanAZPJpwXkrA1wScn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=9bcff3af\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180513/mobile/bkn-20180513040419881-0513_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180513/photo/bkn-20180513040419881-0513_00822_001_02p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180513%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180513040419881-0513_00822_001_02p.jpg&h=caef19f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大家識佢嗎？"},{"pid":"77ad9c46db4bf47c20adc4fa753b056fd2a45b9b","tid":663094,"uid":44117,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T04:04:40.000Z","msg":"正仆街"},{"pid":"3a1745b09d9568963596c035317984514d619c5d","tid":663094,"uid":177219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T04:05:08.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"d0c4ed0f105d3d72017d103dbc6473ecb6b4269d","tid":663094,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T04:06:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40bcd85b93fe613b84f38c302cb5be2eef97a1eb","tid":663094,"uid":47359,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T04:06:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五毛waiwaiwai日日post咸濕新聞<br />\n關鍵時刻現形<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/11/084455_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F11%2F084455_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=8efb265e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"f910f634dca4c3384e82c061d682cc782e5c0bf2","tid":663094,"uid":36049,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T04:07:07.000Z","msg":"又要人起底又遮樣係咩玩法黎"},{"pid":"ea75e2ee79612f1fefbf15243539c2ec9b79cf80","tid":663094,"uid":41969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f910f634dca4c3384e82c061d682cc782e5c0bf2","tid":663094,"uid":36049,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T04:07:07.000Z","msg":"又要人起底又遮樣係咩玩法黎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T04:11:00.000Z","msg":"原post地址都有埋"},{"pid":"5b0b0bca5fabbe7436e6cbea0509df4c98417338","tid":663094,"uid":4811,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T04:29:24.000Z","msg":"無買保險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84309dcf34604a90cb9b9a9ed0b156b66c2ebcba","tid":663094,"uid":72457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T04:32:51.000Z","msg":"雖然係人渣，但台灣人可以點做"},{"pid":"559e601e12